messages.message: I'm trying to do the same thing with the same tables in two different build projects but the responses are very different. First project is here (https://aihub.instabase.com/build/01932709-97c5-700b-95ee-12f2a9f05dd3) and the second project is here (https://aihub.instabase.com/build/0195d3aa-d47b-790a-9d4a-bb2d6f09ca28). The first one is the desired output

oof i do not think we've designed our cleaning prompt pipeline to handle such long cleaning prompts

so i'd recommend
1. using a custom function to do this instead
2. OR trying a derived field
    a. you may run into the same issue though since the derived field pipeline is similar to the cleaning prompt pipeline :sweat:
